{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/studio-theme-zoom-images-with-arrows","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1830,"date":"2022-10-25T11:35:54","date_gmt":"2022-10-25T11:35:54","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1830"},"modified":"2022-10-25T11:35:57","modified_gmt":"2022-10-25T11:35:57","slug":"studio-theme-zoom-images-with-arrows","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/studio-theme-zoom-images-with-arrows/","title":{"rendered":"Studio theme: zoom images with arrows (desktop &#038; mobile)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Studio theme comes with a &#8220;click-to-zoom&#8221; button which users can use to view a bigger version of product images.<br><br>While helpful, one known issue, specially common when using mobile devices, is that the corners of the picture are sometimes cropped. In this quick guide I&#8217;ll teach you both how to fix the size of the zoomed images, as well as how to add arrows to them so that users have a better experience while browsing your store and its products.<br><br>If you&#8217;re wondering what the final result looks like, you can see it here: <a href=\"https://studio-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/ezfy-zoom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-code-files\">Downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can download the code files <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/studio-theme-zoom-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">clicking here</a>. (<a href=\"https://studio-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/ezfy-zoom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-the-code\">Getting the code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>> <strong>Actions </strong>> <strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1271\" height=\"423\" class=\"wp-image-1844\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1.png\" alt=\"Opening the code editor from the Shopify store admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1.png 1271w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1-850x283.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1-1200x399.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1-768x256.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1271px) 100vw, 1271px\" /><br></li><li>Inside the <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/studio-theme-zoom-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">.zip you downloaded</a> there is the following file: <br><strong>ezfy-zoom.txt</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-creating-the-file-for-the-code\">Creating the file for the code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>ezfy-zoom.txt </strong>file and copy the contents in its entirety.</li><li>Go back to your Shopify code editor and in the <strong>Snippets</strong> folder click on &#8220;<em>Add a new snippet</em>&#8220;. <br><br>Name it exactly: <strong>ezfy-zoom</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1401\" height=\"698\" class=\"wp-image-894\" style=\"width: 650px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1.png 1401w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-600x299.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-1200x598.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom1-768x383.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1401px) 100vw, 1401px\" /><br></li><li>Paste the code that you copied previously and after that click on <strong>save</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1564\" height=\"438\" class=\"wp-image-896\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2.jpg 1564w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-600x168.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-1200x336.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-768x215.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-2-1536x430.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1564px) 100vw, 1564px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Final step: including the code to your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the file named <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Inside it, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and use the search bar to look for:<br><br><strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong></li><li>Paste the code below&nbsp;<strong>before&nbsp;</strong>the&nbsp;<strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong>&nbsp;tag you found and then click on save:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-zoom' %}</code></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"720\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-898\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3.jpg 720w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ezfy-zoom-3-600x582.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is all you needed to do! You can now click on the magnifying glass icon found in any of your product page images and the picture will zoom in.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-2 wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"></div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Improved zoom for your product pictures without cropping issues, as well as arrows for better navigation. Works on desktop and mobile.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":1849,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[646],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-zoom-slider-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-zoom-slider-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-zoom-slider-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Studio Theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/studio-zoom-slider.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1830"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1830"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1830/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1860,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1830/revisions/1860"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1849"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://w